## § 2 — Data Quality Checklist

Before using any external data in analysis or as model input:

- [ ] Source confirmed (primary source preferred over secondary)
- [ ] Date range covers the required period
- [ ] Missing values assessed — handling approach documented
- [ ] Outliers reviewed — not silently dropped
- [ ] Units, currency, and encoding confirmed

